annotation.p: Andrzej Sapkowski is one of those rare authors whose works not only gained cult status in our country, but also became part of Russian science fiction. Moreover, Sapkowski is a writer with the talent to create completely original fantasy, completely connected with the classical mythological tradition.

Sapkowski's books are not just brilliant in literary form and depth of content. They are a picture of the world - the world of "sword and magic", the world of sparkling humor, not only capturing the reader's attention, but touching his soul.
